extends layout

block content
  .container
    h1 FreeCodeCamp API Basejump: Image Search Abstraction Layer
    
    h2 User Stories:
      ul
      li 1) I can get the image URLs, alt text and page urls for a set of images relating to a given search string.
      li 2) I can paginate through the responses by adding a ?offset=2 parameter to the URL.
      li 3) I can get a list of the most recently submitted search strings.